    <description>Descend (Day Ability): Can hear dead chat the next night, but can&#39;t use night abilities during the night it is active. Can&#39;t be used until D4 [1 Use]

CW will have a separate chat for this, and can still see dead chat if jailed or linked.


This ability will hopefully help balance out the NK win rate, and will make CW/Sage be a little more helpful/usable, and/or Give Evil classes more claim space/be less suspicious if implemented

As usual, I&#39;m very open to feedback. Fire away!</description>
    
